Package: SPARROT
Title: SPARROT: Spatial Proximity Analysis of Regional Relationships, Overlap, and Transcriptome
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Xu", 
           family = "Pan", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "panx9623@gmail.com")
Description: Tools to quantify and visualize spatial proximity, overlap, and transcriptomic relationships between cell types in spatial transcriptomics data. Supports Seurat integration, cell probability binarization, overlap metrics with permutation testing, nearest-neighbor distance analysis, and multi-celltype visualization.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: 
    methods,
    ggplot2,
    mclust,
    viridisLite,
    S4Vectors,
    Matrix,
    Seurat,
    concaveman,
    ggnewscale,
    cowplot,
    Nebulosa,
    fields,
    colorspace
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
